Battera::

She walked away from Cybershark and walked back to the entrance of the ship. 
  She transformed back into bat mode and flew off.  She headed shyward and 
flew over the forest.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

DarkMouse::

She looked at the scanner and saw a figure moving over the base.
"Quickstrike, take a look.  We have someone flying overhead.  Want to sent 
someone for a look-see? the signal shows Predacon.  But it's not one of 
ours."
